turns and stirs up a giant wave. As for HAU YEE's murderer is someone unexpected, and because of this the Poon's family business is faced with retribution. Thus, YEUNG and BING BING were determined to be the property protectors...","tmdb_id":84734,"cast":["Mã Tuấn Vỹ","Dương Thiến Nghiêu","Mạch Trường Thanh","Thiệu Mỹ Kỳ","Natalie Tong","Tào Vĩnh Liêm","Mat Yeung","Nhạc Hoa","Trình Khả Vi","Lý Quốc Lân","Trương Quốc Cường","Katy Kung","Rachel Kan","Tracy Ip","Khang Hoa"],"director":[],"keywords":[],"tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"84734","season":1,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0},"cast_meta":[{"name":"Mã Tuấn Vỹ","name_vi":"Mã Tuấn Vỹ","name_original":"Steven Ma Chun-Wai","tmdb_id":1233285,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/q60svjeSi9KpyZCwhnwwy6iy8Qs.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1233285"},{"name":"Dương Thiến Nghiêu","name_vi":"Dương Thiến Nghiêu","name_original":"Tavia Yeung","tmdb_id":1222259,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tuvy2JTxuYPzkS6YqYJ0RvOlPlE.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1222259"},{"name":"Mạch Trường Thanh","name_vi":"Mạch Trường Thanh","name_original":"Evergreen Mak Cheung-Ching","tmdb_id":985094,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/u1lUv0JR4v0gNXjUWtfPJ43I8SA.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/985094"},{"name":"Thiệu Mỹ Kỳ","name_vi":"Thiệu Mỹ Kỳ","name_original":"Maggie Shiu Mei-Kei","tmdb_id":1173600,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/smUbYgh0zhsCba0nz8Nmb3ODOeP.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1173600"},{"name":"Natalie Tong","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Natalie Tong","tmdb_id":1237978,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jZHpp0BOnVW3M0NqH3TVpj0oGo6.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1237978"},{"name":"Tào Vĩnh Liêm","name_vi":"Tào Vĩnh Liêm","name_original":"Raymond Cho Wing-Lim","tmdb_id":1223053,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pU3V6I4xp4wIGRix7wibb5ga4wk.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/12